{
  "text": "Our result [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] actually applies to a larger class of logically defined regular tree languages, based on the use of Lindstr\u00f6m quantifiers. First-order logic is thus a particular case of our result, which also yields (for instance) an algebraic characterization of first-order logic with modular quantifiers added.",
  "correct_citation": {
